%h3 Hey here you can find lists of expenses shared with you:

- @shared_expenses.each do |shared_expense|
  .card.mt-2
    .card-body.d-inline-flex.justify-content-around
      =link_to "#{shared_expense.sender.email}", expense_sharing_path(shared_expense)


%h3 You share your expenses with:
- @sent_expenses.each do |sent_expense|
  .card.mt-2
    .card-body.d-inline-flex.justify-content-around
      %p= sent_expense.recipient.email
      = button_to "Stop share", expense_sharing_path(sent_expense), method: :delete , class: 'btn btn-danger'
